<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ PROJECT INDEX ═══ -->
<section class="section" id="proj-index">
  <div class="section-label">18 — Codebase Indexing</div>
  <h2 class="section-title"><span class="icon">🗂️</span>Project Index</h2>

  <div class="info-box">
    Built at session startup and cached in <code>.gondola_index.json</code>. Scans the workspace up to 6 levels deep, extracts per-file symbols and summaries, and compresses the entire codebase to ~1000 tokens for the system prompt.
  </div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--cyan);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">Symbol Extraction</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Python: classes and functions with line numbers. JS/TS: exports and function declarations. Summary auto-generated from docstring, filename patterns (test_, config, utils, etc.), or symbol counts.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--green);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">Change Detection</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Each file entry stores a content hash. On the next session start, modified files are re-indexed while unchanged files are loaded from cache — keeping startup fast even on large codebases.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--yellow);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">Task Keyword Matching</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Files are classified into semantic categories: <em>settings, auth, ui, api, database, test, style</em>. When a user says "find the settings file", the relevant group is surfaced first without a full search.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--blue);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">Semantic Search</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Optional embedding vectors via <code>sentence_transformers</code>. When available, <code>semantic_search()</code> returns file relevance scores against a natural-language query rather than keyword matching.</div>
      <div class="card-meta"><span class="tag blue">optional</span><span class="tag blue">sentence_transformers</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--magenta);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">Ignore Patterns</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Skips: <code>.git</code>, <code>node_modules</code>, <code>.venv</code>, <code>dist</code>, <code>build</code>, <code>.next</code>, <code>.gondola_backups</code>, <code>.gondola_knowledge</code>, images, <code>*.pyc</code>, <code>*.min.js</code>, <code>*.log</code>, <code>package-lock.json</code>.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--orange);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">Dependency Mapping</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Local imports detected per file and stored in the index. Used by <code>smart_context(filename, depth=2)</code> to automatically surface related files — callers, imports, tests — without manual searching.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

