  <h2 class="section-title"><span class="icon">📁</span>Workspace Management</h2>

  <div class="info-box">
    Gondola supports multiple workspaces with independent memory, indexes, and GONDOLA.md files. Switching workspaces reinitializes all subsystems <strong>without clearing conversation history</strong> — the agent retains context of what it was doing.
  </div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--cyan);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">Persistence</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Active workspace path written to <code>.workspace_config</code> on every switch. Restored on startup via <code>load_saved_workspace()</code>. Falls back to the default <code>sandbox_dir</code> if the file is missing.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--green);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">Workspace Switching</div>
      <div class="card-desc"><code>POST /api/workspace</code> accepts a path (supports <code>~</code> and env vars). Calls <code>initialize(clear_messages=False)</code> — reinits ContextManager, ProjectIndex, MemoryV2, and tool subsystems with the new root, but leaves the message history intact.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--yellow);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">Workspace Discovery</div>
      <div class="card-desc"><code>GET /api/workspaces</code> enumerates siblings of the parent directory and returns them with <code>name</code>, <code>path</code>, and <code>is_current</code> flags. Powers the workspace dropdown in Daft UI.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--magenta);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">Per-Workspace State</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Each workspace maintains its own: <code>GONDOLA.md</code>, <code>.gondola_memory/</code> daily files, <code>.gondola_index.json</code>, <code>.gondola_tags</code>, <code>.personality_config</code>, <code>.gondola_backups/</code>. Nothing bleeds between workspaces.</div>
